	('f1eb521d-f979-4523-b24e-e57431a1c64c', 'Cornwall & Seaside Nostalgia Gift Buyer', 'UK-based adult who loves Cornwall and seaside towns, regularly buys thoughtful gifts online, and is drawn to comfortable slip-ons with scenic artwork (Cornish seaside town). Purchases are often for birthdays, Mother’s/Father’s Day, Christmas, or as a ‘little reminder of the coast’.', 'Consumer (B2C) - Gifts & Home Comfort', 'N/A (individual consumer)', 'United Kingdom (England: Cornwall, Devon, Somerset, Dorset)', '{"Most slippers online feel bland; few have UK coastal artwork that sparks nostalgia","Uncertainty about sizing/fit for a gift recipient, especially for slip-ons","Worry that printed artwork will fade or look cheap in real life","Gift purchases get delayed when shipping times aren’t clear or dispatch is slow","Hard to judge comfort and warmth from product photos alone"}', '{"Buy a gift that feels personal and place-based (Cornish seaside town artwork) rather than generic footwear","Find slippers that are easy to slip on/off for around-the-house wear","Choose a gift that looks premium enough to give without needing extra explanation","Get delivery in time for a specific occasion with clear shipping updates","Avoid hassle with sizing by using a straightforward size guide and easy exchanges"}', '£30–£55 per pair; up to £90 for two pairs when gifting', '{"Self (buyer)","Partner/spouse (influencer for joint gifting decisions)"}', '{"iPhone/Android mobile browsing",Instagram,Facebook,"Google Search","Apple Pay/Google Pay","Royal Mail/standard UK courier tracking"}', '{"Choosing the right size when buying as a gift and wanting it to fit first time","Trusting comfort/quality without trying on","Needing quick answers on dispatch, returns, and exchange timelines","Finding something ‘Cornwall-coded’ without it looking touristy"}', '{"Occasion-led bundles (gift bag, gift message, ‘Seaside Gift Set’)","UGC and reviews showing the artwork detail and how they look on-foot","Clear fit g