	('83557a9c-46d8-47d8-a84f-8a942fd30a4c', 'Value-Seeking Everyday Online Shopper', 'Price-conscious consumer who regularly buys online and is willing to try new DTC brands like afa if the offer is clear, low-risk, and competitively priced.', 'Consumer (B2C eCommerce)', 'N/A (individual consumer)', 'United States (suburban and mid-sized metro areas)', '{"Abandons checkout when shipping costs/taxes appear late in the process","Skeptical of unknown brands due to fear of low quality or poor support","Frustrated by confusing product descriptions that don’t answer practical questions","Annoyed by long delivery windows or unclear fulfillment updates"}', '{"Find a reliable qef option that meets basic needs without overpaying","Minimize risk when trying a new brand (easy returns, clear warranty, transparent policies)","Complete purchases quickly on mobile with minimal steps and no surprise fees","Get predictable delivery timelines and tracking"}', 'USD 25–80 per order; comfortable trying with first-order discount up to USD 15', '{"Self (primary buyer)","Spouse/partner (influencer on household spending)"}', '{"iPhone/Android smartphone","Mobile wallets (Apple Pay, Google Pay)","Gmail/Outlook email","Instagram and Facebook","Amazon (for price comparison)"}', '{"Needs fast trust-building signals (reviews, guarantees, social proof) to purchase from afa","Low patience for slow sites, multi-step checkout, or forced account creation","High sensitivity to total landed cost and delivery date"}', '{"First-purchase incentive + free shipping threshold to lift conversion","Short-form product pages with clear benefits, sizing/specs, and FAQs","Post-purchase tracking + proactive support messaging to reduce refund requests","Bundles to increase perceived value while protecting margins"}', '2026-01-27 17:10:43.797+00', '2026-01-27 17:10:43.797+00', '155ee0b1-3a3c-4a24-a836-14ddafc0f3b5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '6f545bc2-4baa-4a8e-b51c-365e8797931e'),
	('2138e26f-0c2e-4c5d-9247-6575b9a227b7', 'Convenience-Driven Repeat Buyer (Time-Poor Professional)', 'Busy professional who shops online for convenience, prefers brands that remove friction, and will reorder qef if the experience is consistent and delivery is dependable.', 'Consumer (B2C eCommerce)', 'N/A (individual consumer)', 'United States (major metros and surrounding commuter regions)', '{"Hates product pages that bury key info (dimensions, materials, compatibility, care/use instructions)","Doesn’t trust brands with slow customer support or unclear return policies","Avoids checkout flows without fast-pay options","Gets frustrated when items go out of stock and there’s no back-in-stock alert"}', '{"Buy qef quickly with minimal decision fatigue (clear variants, simple choices)","Get consistent quality so they don’t have to research alternatives each time","Receive fast shipping and reliable delivery estimates","Use subscriptions or reorder links to avoid repeat checkout effort"}', 'USD 60–150 per order; open to subscription/reorder spend of USD 40–120 per month', '{"Self (primary buyer)","Household co-decision maker (partner/spouse) for recurring purchases"}', '{"iPhone/Android smartphone","Apple Pay/Google Pay/Shop Pay","Email + SMS","Instagram, YouTube (how-to/reviews)","Google Search"}', '{"Needs reassurance that afa can deliver consistently (inventory, shipping SLAs, support responsiveness)","Requires clear differentiation vs. marketplaces to justify switching","Low tolerance for complicated product selection or unclear variant naming"}', '{"One-click reorder, subscription option, and replenishment reminders via SMS/email","Back-in-stock alerts and pre-order options to capture demand","Speed messaging (shipping cutoffs, delivery estimates) and trust badges to reduce hesitation","Loyalty perks that reward repeat buying (points, free expedited shipping thresholds)"}', '2026-01-27 17:10:43.797+00', '2026-01-27 17:10:43.797+00', '155ee0b1-3a3c-4a24-a836-14ddafc