	('39325c53-81b6-4044-8581-658051b4da95', 'Trend-Influenced Social Shopper (Discovery-Led)', 'Social-first shopper who discovers new products through creators and short-form video, buys qef based on perceived fit/lifestyle alignment, and responds strongly to UGC and limited-time drops.', 'Consumer (B2C eCommerce)', 'N/A (individual consumer)', 'United States (coastal and high-social-engagement urban areas)', '{"Doubts authenticity when reviews look generic or overly polished","Gets annoyed when the product shown in videos doesn’t match the listing or variants","Bounces if the landing page doesn’t immediately match the social ad promise","Worries about being stuck with something if returns are difficult"}', '{"Discover qef that feels new/interesting and matches their identity or aesthetic","See real-world proof (UGC, creator demos, before/after, unboxings) before buying","Get a smooth mobile checkout directly from social platforms","Share purchases and recommendations with friends/followers"}', 'USD 30–120 per order; impulse-buy threshold around USD 40–70 with a limited-time offer', '{"Self (primary buyer)","Friends/online community (strong influence through comments and shares)"}', '{"iPhone/Android smartphone","TikTok, Instagram Reels, Snapchat","Creator affiliate links and discount codes","Mobile wallet checkout (Apple Pay/Google Pay)","SMS for drop alerts"}', '{"Requires a steady flow of fresh creative and UGC to maintain attention","High expectation that product experience matches creator content","Sensitive to negative comments; needs proactive reputation and community management"}', '{"Creator seeding + affiliate program to generate credible UGC at scale","Dedicated landing pages per creator/ad angle to improve conversion","Limited-time bundles/drops and SMS waitlists to drive urgency","Post-purchase share incentives (refer-a-friend credit, UGC contests) to fuel organic growth"}', '2026-01-27 17:10:43.797+00', '2026-01-27 17:10:43.797+00', '155ee0b1-3a3c-4a24-